==Description==

The '''BIM Clone''' tool is a shortcut to the standard [[Draft_Clone|Draft Clone]] tool, but launches a [[Draft_Move|Draft Move]] command just after cloning, thus allowing you to clone and place the cloned object somewhere else in the model in one go.


